fi.marketing.list.logic

Class Consent

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.marketing.list.logic.Consent

  • public class Consent
extends Object
    Consents have each their own lifespan of two years from the latest consent. One customer might have several consents and each of these have different timestamps. It is important to know where (=what campaign) and when (=when campaign was generated) the consents were used.
